### Overview

This indicator measures the energy efficiency of non - domestic property by expressing the proportion of properties which have an energy rating of A or A+, in other words the best performing properties. Data are sourced from the [Ministry of Housing, Communities and Local Government](https://get-energy-performance-data.communities.gov.uk/).


